
## Features
- User registration and login
- Service listing
- Firebase integration for data storage

## Setup Instructions
1. Clone the repository.
2. Replace Firebase configuration in `firebase-config.js` with your own.
3. Open `index.html` in your browser.

## Logging
All actions are logged in the console for tracking user actions.

## Deployment
This application can be hosted on Firebase Hosting or any other cloud platform.

## How to Contribute
Feel free to fork the repository and submit pull requests.
Conclusion
This implementation provides a foundational structure for the Digital E Gram Panchayat project. You can expand upon this by adding more features such as user roles (admin, staff), application status tracking, and service management functionalities as outlined in the problem statement. Make sure to test all functionalities and maintain the code in a public GitHub repository.